			name: "module-12-title",
			type: "title",
			script: "In Module 06 we looked at enterprise use cases and value drivers. But we didn't fully address the risks: prompt injection, misuse, and the need for human oversight. Agents that act autonomously can act wrongly. How do you keep them controllable, auditable, and resistant to manipulation? This module covers human-in-the-loop approval workflows, prompt injection defenses, and compliance basics. It's how you operate agents responsibly.",
